title: How much of the locked LP rewards should get burned?
body: There are many ideas from the community regarding what to do with 80% of the locked LP rewards.  As a starting point, I feel we should establish how much of it to burn.  As far as the remainder, how to use those rewards can be decided in a future vote.
author: 0xe9B7064BC3D5c4A4a701f7d785445cA68B32D0C2
